replies.body: Same issue - logged in to mention it - PLEASE HELP RIOT - I just played last night with no problems... woke up to this.  Already tried uninstalling and re-installing from scratch to no effect.
someone get this OP an award because he is {{champion:497}}

I have tried hextech tool. Updating windows. Running as Admin. Riot what is going on it's an infinite loop it's been 1 hour I was logged out of the client just as i won my diamond 5 promos (god bless). But still, there's no way of logging back in. I can't even initiate a full repair with the client tool because the gear button is out of reach and cannot be clicked. Help please

THIS IS EXACTLY WHAT IS HAPPENING TO ME RIGHT NOW!!!! I HAVE BEEN PLAYING ALL MORNING. AND I GET OUT OF A GAME AND THEN THIS IS WHAT HAPPENS... IT WORKED FOR LITERALLY THREE MINUTES AFTER THE FIRST TIME AND NOW ITS ALL THAT IT DOES... I SUBMITTED A TICKET BUT HAVE HEARD NOTHING BACK FROM THEM..
riot hasn't admited there's an issue, they will comment we need to run the hextech repair tool.  even tho there are scores of individual people with the issue.  it's clearly on their end.
